tps:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/yusuf-son-yaqub-ishaq-ibrahim\/","url_meta":{"origin":34747,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Yusuf: The nobleman, son of the noblemen","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe nobleman, son of the nobleman, son of the nobleman, son of the nobleman. That was Joseph, son of Jacob, son of Isaac, son of Abraham, upon them be peace.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3202 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":927,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/18\/yusuf-ihsan-deen-fiqh\/","url_meta":{"origin":34747,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Fiqh: Excellence in Islam requires understanding","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: It was said to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhich people are the most noble?'' The Prophet said, \u201cThe most noble to Allah are the most righteous.\u201d They said, \u201cThat is not what we are asking about.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe most noble of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2796,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/ibrahim-abraham-best-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":34747,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ibrahim: Prophet Abraham is best of creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO best of creation!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat is Abraham, upon him be peace.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2369 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u00a0\u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37922,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/abraham-qalb-salim\/","url_meta":{"origin":34747,"position":3},"title":"\u2018Urwah on Ibrahim: Abraham never cursed anyone, his heart was pure","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham reported: \u2018Urwah ibn al-Zubayr, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cO my son, do not fall into the habit of cursing others. Have you not seen that Abraham never cursed anyone? As Allah said: When he came to his Lord with a pure heart.\u201d (37:84) Source: Tafsi\u0304r al-T\u0323abari\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":718,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/